    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. For the lesson though, I want to make sure I'm being thorough. Some people argue that the whole idea of 'substantive' due process is actually pretty problematic and that the court should stick strictly to 'procedural' due process instead. Could you explain why they feel that way so I can present both perspectives?",
